        <p>A bit further into Yosemite Valley you can admire the <strong>Majestic Yosemite Hotel</strong> (formerly the Ahwanee), a massive upscale lodge-like hotel that you can explore without a reservation. Among the hotel's most famous features is its grand dining room.</p>
